-- Cypriot finance minister resigns
-- 
-- Tue Apr 2, 2013 8:20am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/04/02/us-cyprus-minister-idUSBRE9310E920130402

 

 NICOSIA  (Reuters) - Cypriot Finance Minister Michael Sarris said he resigned on Tuesday, after concluding talks with foreign lenders on a bailout that forced the island to impose heavy losses on bank depositors in return for aid. 
 (Reporting by  Michele Kambas , Writing by Deepa Babington)